name: The Vulcana Singlet
description:
The Vulcana singlet

Select a colour from three options - perfect for everyday wear.

- Flattering racer back style
- Lightweight breathable material
- Available in three colours: 
black (back view), pink (front view), army grey/green (front view)
- Front: VULCANA WOMEN'S CIRCUS
- Back: VULCANISTA www.vulcana.org.au with illustration

All proceeds excluding shipping cost go to 1000 Women Strong.
To support us or find out more: bit.ly/HzM4YW

Postage within Australia via Regular Parcel Post. For overseas shipping, please contact us for a postage estimate.

If you have any questions please don’t hesitate to contact us and we will get back to you as soon as possible.

name: Two Limited Edition Vulcana Tote Bags for $40
description:
Pick two designs from a range of limited edition Vulcana tote bags perfect for every day use as a reuseable bag for your groceries, laptop, books or gym gear.

- Each bag has been lovingly screenprinted by hand by friends of the Vulcana community (the bag you receive may not be the same as the photo as each bag is 100% unique with it's own small set of charming imperfections)
- Dimensions approx. 42 long x 37cm wide (easily fits a 15" laptop)
- Double handles 40cm x 2.5cm
- 100% cotton calico material - gentle spot clean recommended

Original artwork donated by local Brisbane designers for Vulcana (from top left clockwise):
- "She believed she could so she did" by Davina Purnama - RED ONLY
- "We Are All Made Of Stars" by Vivian Van Balen - BLACK OR RED
- "Goodbye I'm Off To Join The Circus" by Davina Purnama  - BLACK OR RED
- "Everything will be ok... in the meantime here are a bunch of cats!" by Grace Law - RED ONLY
- "We never know how high we are till we are called to rise, and then if we are true to form our statures touch the skies. - Emily Dickinson" by Clare Bailey - BLACK OR RED
- "She Stood In The Storm And When The Wind Did Not Blow Her Away She Adjusted Her Sails. - Elizabeth Edwards" by Davina Purnama - BLACK OR RED

PLEASE NOTE: Before purchasing, please email us with the two designs you would like and the colours you'd prefer for each design (black or red) and we will let you know if we have that particular design in the colour you prefer.

Once you have received confirmation that we have the designs and the colours you want, then proceed to checkout and comment again to confirm in the "Note To Seller" section the two designs and respective colours you would like.

All proceeds excluding shipping cost go to 1000 Women Strong.
To support us or find out more: bit.ly/HzM4YW

Postage within Australia via Regular Parcel Post. For overseas shipping, please contact us for a postage estimate.

If you have any questions please don’t hesitate to contact us and we will get back to you as soon as possible.

Keep in touch with us:

Instagram: @circusvulcana
Twitter: twitter.com/CircusVulcana
